description: Moves Maps Accounts from one ResourceGroup (or Subscription) to another

move_request.description: The details of the Maps Account move.

message.description: If available, a human readable description of the error.

target.description: If available, the component generating the error.

details.description: If available, a list of additional details about the error.

subscription_id.description: Subscription credentials which uniquely identify Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group that contains Maps Account to move.
